snippet.title: World of Stickman Classic RTS PC 2024 Announcement
snippet.description:
World of Stickman - classic war strategy with stickman heroes. Collect resources, build your base and hire a powerful army.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1922500/World_of_Stickman_Classic_RTS/

Choose from 3 available races: Romans, Egyptians or Vikings.

Fight with players from all over the world in Online mode.

Immerse yourself in the adventures of the Stickmen, completing tasks in a single company
